luôn đi?

4
00:05:14,910 --> 00:05:16,450
Nhanh!

5
00:05:16,450 --> 00:05:18,910
Dậy nhanh... nhanh đi rửa mặt đi.

6
00:05:20,210 --> 00:05:22,210
Nhanh lên!

7
00:05:23,290 --> 00:05:25,290
